  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the magical world of Love Letters: First Bloom, where the challenge of word games meets the serenity of a spring garden. Create your own quiet corner where your mind can freely wander through the garden of words.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Word game available in 8 languages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Mysterious blocks reveal hidden letters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Locked letters unlock when adjacent words are solved</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Engaging pattern matching puzzle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play with mouse or keyboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Relaxing background music accompanies your journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Infinite unique puzzles in every new game</p>",
